\c 35
\s Ukugcinwa kwephasika
\p
\v 1 UJosiya wasesenzela iN\nd kosi\nd* iphasika eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 23.21.\x*; basebehlaba iphasika ngolwetshumi lane lwenyanga yokuqala\x + Eks. 12.6. Ezra 6.19.\x*.
\v 2 Wasemisa abapristi kumfanelo zabo, wabaqinisela inkonzo yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 31.4.\x*.
\v 3 Wasesithi kumaLevi ayefundisa uIsrayeli wonke ayengcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 15.3. 17.8,9. 30.22. Neh. 8.7,9. Levi 10.11. Dute. 17.9. 33.10. Ezra 7.10. Hag. 2.11. Mal. 2.7.\x*: Fakani umtshokotsho ongcwele\x + 34.14.\x* endlini uSolomoni indodana kaDavida inkosi yakoIsrayeli ayakhayo\x + 5.7.\x*; kaku\add se\add*ngumthwalo kini emahlombe. Khathesi khonzani iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu labantu bayo uIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 23.26.\x*.
\v 4 Njalo li\add zi\add*lungise ngokwendlu yaboyihlo ngezigaba zenu\x + 1 Lan. 9.9.\x*, njengombhalo kaDavida inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 23,24,25,26.\x* lanjengombhalo kaSolomoni indodana yakhe\x + 8.14.\x*.
\v 5 Lime endaweni engcwele\x + Hlab. 134.1.\x* ngokwezigaba zendlu yaboyise babafowenu, abantwana besizwe, lesigaba sendlu kayise wamaLevi\x + 35.12. Ezra 6.18.\x*.
\v 6 Lihlabe iphasika, lizingcwelise, lilungisele abafowenu, ukwenza njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi\x + 29.5,15,34. 30.3,15. 1 Lan. 15.12. Ezra 6.20.\x*.
\p
\v 7 UJosiya wasenika abantwana babantu umhlambi wamawundlu lamazinyane embuzi, konke kungokwamaphasika\x + 30.17.\x*, kwabo bonke abatholakalayo, ngenani eliyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu, lenkunzi ezizinkulungwane ezintathu; lokhu kwakuvela empahleni yenkosi\x + 31.3.\x*.
\v 8 Iziphathamandla zakhe zasezinika abantu, abapristi lamaLevi ngokukhululeka. OHilikhiya\x + 34.9.\x* loZekhariya loJehiyeli\x + 34.12.\x*, izinduna zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, banikelela amaphasika\x + 30.17.\x* kubapristi \add amazinyane\add* azinkulungwane ezimbili lamakhulu ayisithupha, lenkunzi ezingamakhulu amathathu\x + 35.7.\x*.
\v 9 OKonaniya\x + 31.12,13.\x* loShemaya loNethaneli, abafowabo\x + 31.12,13.\x*, loHashabhiya loJeyiyeli loJozabadi, izinduna zamaLevi, basebenikelela amaphasika\x + 30.17.\x* kumaLevi \add amazinyane\add* azinkulungwane ezinhlanu, lenkunzi ezingamakhulu amahlanu\x + 35.7.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ngokunjalo inkonzo yalungiswa; abapristi basebesima endaweni yabo\x + 30.16.\x*, lamaLevi ngezigaba zawo, njengokomlayo wenkosi\x + Ezra 6.18.\x*.
\v 11 Basebehlaba iphasika\x + 30.15. Ezra 6.20.\x*, abapristi bafafaza kuvela ezandleni zabo\x + 29.22.\x*, lamaLevi ahlinza\x + 29.34.\x*.
\v 12 Basebesusa \add i\add*m\add i\add*nikelo yokutshiswa ukuyinika njengokwezigaba zendlu yaboyise kubantwana babantu ukuze banikele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, njengokubhaliweyo egwalweni lukaMozisi. Ngokunjalo langezinkunzi.
\v 13 Basebesosa iphasika ngomlilo njengokwesimiso\x + Eks. 12.8,9. Dute. 16.7.\x*; kodwa izinto ezingcwele bazipheka\x + Eks. 12.8,9. Dute. 16.7.\x* ngamabhodo\x + 2 Kho. 4.38.\x* langezimbiza\x + 1 Sam. 2.14. Jobe 41.20.\x* langezindengezi\x + 2 Kho. 21.13.\x*, bakusa masinyane kubo bonke abantwana babantu.
\v 14 Lemva kwalokho basebezilungisela bona labapristi, ngoba abapristi amadodana kaAroni babesekunikeleni iminikelo yokutshiswa lamahwahwa kwaze kwaba sebusuku\x + Levi 3.14,17.\x*; ngakho amaLevi azilungisela wona labapristi amadodana kaAroni.
\v 15 Labahlabeleli amadodana kaAsafi babesendaweni yabo njengokomlayo kaDavida\x + 1 Lan. 25.1.\x*, loAsafi, loHemani, loJeduthuni umboni wenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*; labagcini bamasango babesesangweni lonke\x + 1 Lan. 9.17,18. 26.13.\x*; kwakungesikwabo ukusuka enkonzweni yabo, ngoba abafowabo amaLevi abalungisela\x + 35.14.\x*.
\v 16 Yasilungiswa yonke inkonzo yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngalolosuku ukwenza iphasika lokunikela iminikelo yokutshiswa phezu kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd*, njengokomlayo wenkosi uJosiya.
\v 17 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli ababekhona basebesenza iphasika ngalesosikhathi, lomkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo, insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Ezra 6.22.\x*.
\v 18 Njalo kalenziwanga iphasika elinjengaleli\x + 2 Kho. 23.22,23.\x* koIsrayeli kusukela ensukwini zikaSamuweli umprofethi\x + 30.13-27. 2 Kho. 23.22.\x*; lawo wonke amakhosi akoIsrayeli kawenzanga iphasika elinje uJosiya alenzayo, labapristi lamaLevi, loJuda loIsrayeli wonke ababekhona, labahlali beJerusalema.
\v 19 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lesificaminwembili wokubusa kukaJosiya iphasika leli lenziwa\x + 21.2.\x*.
\s Ukufa kukaJosiya
\p
\v 20 Emva kwakho konke lokho, uJosiya eseyilungisile indlu, uNeko inkosi yeGibhithe\x + 2 Kho. 23.29.\x* wenyuka uku\add ya\add*kulwa leKarikemeshi eYufrathi\x + Isa. 10.9. Jer. 46.2.\x*; loJosiya waphuma uku\add ya\add*melana laye.
\v 21 Kodwa wathuma izithunywa kuye esithi: Ngilani lawe, nkosi yakoJuda? Kangenyukelanga ukumelana lawe wena lamuhla, kodwa ngimelene lendlu elwa lami\x + 2 Sam. 16.10.\x*. Ngoba uNkulunkulu uthe ngiphangise; yekela wena \add ukuphikisana\add* loNkulunkulu, olami, ukuze angakubhubhisi\x + 25.16. Eks. 14.12.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uJosiya kaphendulanga ubuso bakhe kuye\x + 29.6.\x*, kodwa wazifihla isimo ukuze alwe laye\x + 1 Sam. 28.8.\x*; njalo kawalalelanga amazwi kaNeko avela emlonyeni kaNkulunkulu\x + 35.21.\x*, kodwa weza ukulwa esihotsheni\x + Zek. 12.11.\x* seMegido\x + Hlu. 5.19.\x*.
\v 23 Abatshoki bemitshoko basebemciba uJosiya; inkosi yasisithi encekwini zayo: Ngisusani ngoba ngizwa ubuhlungu obukhulu.
\v 24 Inceku zakhe zasezimkhupha enqoleni, zamgadisa enqoleni yesibili ayelayo, zamletha eJerusalema. Wasesifa, wangcwatshelwa emangcwabeni aboyise\x + 2 Kho. 23.30.\x*; wonke uJuda leJerusalema basebemlilela uJosiya\x + Zek. 12.11.\x*.
\p
\v 25 LoJeremiya wenza isililo ngoJosiya\x + 2 Sam. 1.17. Lilo 4.20.\x*. Labo bonke abahlabeleli labahlabelelikazi bakhuluma ngoJosiya ezililweni zabo kuze kube lamuhla\x + 2 Sam. 19.35. Mat. 9.23. Ezra 2.65. Neh. 7.67.\x*. Bazenza zaba yisimiso koIsrayeli; khangela-ke, zibhaliwe ezililweni\x + Hlu. 11.39.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJosiya, lezisa zakhe njengokubhaliweyo emlayweni weN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 27 izindaba zakhe-ke, ezokuqala lezokucina, khangela, zibhaliwe egwalweni lwamakhosi akoIsrayeli lawakoJuda\x + 1 Lan. 29.29.\x*.